premise_source_doc_sentence: JAG  (  U.S. military acronym for Judge Advocate General  )  is an American legal drama television show with a distinct U.S. Navy theme , created by Donald P. Bellisario , and produced by Belisarius Productions in association with Paramount Network Television  (  now CBS Television Studios  )  .
